comments: i have improved so much upon taking this class. at first i would stress out because i knew i was not a very good. now i feel very confident of the sketches i have been doing. jimmy is an excellent teacher and gives very good feedback. as long as you listen to his advice, practice and do your assignments, you will see huge improvement.

Very difficult class but overall very valuable. Success is possible in this class just be sure to keep up on your sketchbook, don\'t turn in any late projects (no matter how tempting it is), show up to class (missing a class most likely means you\'ll miss an in class sketch). Mr. Chang is very helpful and knowledgeable just be sure to ask questions!
